Note that when server names have been switched (databasemanager.switchServer),the real server names must be used here, plugins.rawSQL is not transparent to switched servers. ****************************************************************************/
var uuid = application.getNewUUID(); plugins.rawSQL.executeSQL(databaseManager.getDataSourceServerName(controller.getDataSource()), 'employees', 'insert into employees (employees_id, creation_date) values (?, ?)', [plugins.rawSQL.convertUUIDToBytes(uuid), new Date()]);

